      "content": "wait r u sure? its probably just the hay fever cuz its peak season right now. i dont want to go to the hospital for nothing, it sounds dramatic. honestly the whistling isnt even that bad, it just gets a bit harder to breathe if i move too fast. i'll just take a Zyrtec and a bit of water and lie down for a bit, that should clear it up right?",
